<item>
            <title>[SPARK-51206] Python Data Sources incorrectly imports from Spark Connect</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-51206</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Python Data Source workers plan_data_source_read and write_into_data_source import some arrow/row conversion helpers from pyspark.sql.connect.conversion. The imported helper actually doesn&apos;t need any Spark Connect dependency.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However pyspark.sql.connect.conversion checks for Spark Connect dependencies. This causes failure when using Python Data Source if any of pandas, grpcio, etc. is missing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-python&quot;&gt;
.venv/lib/python3.9/site-packages/pyspark/sql/worker/plan_data_source_read.py:34: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;module&amp;gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; pyspark.sql.connect.conversion &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; ArrowTableToRowsConversion, LocalDataToArrowConversion .venv/lib/python3.9/site-packages/pyspark/sql/connect/conversion.py:20: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;module&amp;gt; check_dependencies(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;__name__&lt;/span&gt;) .venv/lib/python3.9/site-packages/pyspark/sql/connect/utils.py:37: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; check_dependencies require_minimum_grpc_version() .venv/lib/python3.9/site-packages/pyspark/sql/connect/utils.py:49: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;in&lt;/span&gt; require_minimum_grpc_version &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;raise&lt;/span&gt; PySparkImportError( E pyspark.errors.exceptions.base.PySparkImportError: [PACKAGE_NOT_INSTALLED] grpcio &amp;gt;= 1.48.1 must be installed; however, it was &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;not&lt;/span&gt; found.&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
